snippet.title: Wasted Glory Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Gamejolt:
https://gamejolt.com/games/wasted-glory/383191

itch.io: 
https://deerpy.itch.io/wasted-glory

Launch trailer for Wasted Glory, a fnaf fan game i've been working on.

Game description: Wasted Glory is an old-fashioned fnaf fan game that follows the traditional five nights gameplay with freeroam mechanics.
As this is an old fashioned fnaf fan game the models and graphics are older as to give an older feeling to the game.
